*   [Public Lands](/United_States_Senate_Committee_on_Public_Lands) (Chairman: [Robert W. Johnson](/Robert_Ward_Johnson))
*   Retrenchment (Chairman: N/A)
*   [Revolutionary Claims](/United_States_Senate_Committee_on_Revolutionary_Claims) (Chairman: N/A)
*   [Tariff Regulation](/United_States_Senate_Select_Committee_on_the_Tariff_Regulation) (Select)
*   [Territories](/United_States_Senate_Committee_on_Territories) (Chairman: N/A)
*   Thirteen on the Disturbed Condition of the Country (Select), a committee formed explicitly to address the national crisis, a desperate attempt to find common ground that ultimately failed.
